author: Make Something
description:
My extremely unusual shop has a real purpose. Brought to us by Squarespace. For 10% off your first purchase, go to: http://squarespace.com/makesomething

Patreon members get Fusion 360 files, early and ad-free videos, my custom finish, behind the scenes videos, as well as access to our private Discord: https://www.patreon.com/picciuto

This workshop breaks every rule, carpeted floors, hidden tools, no exposed ductwork. And it’s all intentional! This isn’t a space designed for maximum efficiency, it’s designed for comfort, creativity, and wanting to be here. In this video, I walk through my shop, talk about why I made these choices, when efficiency actually matters, and how the environment you work in quietly shapes the way you think and create.
